{
  "stem": "19921.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When my mother didn't want to go, I was the oldest in my house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that nothing will happen to us, go with your uncles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The reason with my uncle was-- were-- my-- my uncle and my aunt, actually, decided to go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just because she decided to go, and she urge everybody to go, because she was thrown out from Germany in 1938.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If she wouldn't have been there-- and by the way, they just came also from vacation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody was on vacation that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had-- they married in February, and they couldn't have a honeymoon because of the time, the season, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they decided to go in the summer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they went on vacation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they just made it, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They just made it a day before I did from [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They just made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And because of her, really, because of her-- and her name was Mona-- is Mona Lehrfeld.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because of her, because she suffered already from German sense, she didn't trust the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The other people, like other my uncle, my mother-- first of all, she had her parents there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She wouldn't leave her parents there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She had a sister there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She wouldn't leave her sister there with the three children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my other uncle, Moniek, she-- they have a baby, and they were fluent in German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He says, we don't have to be afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, we can talk to German people and, you know, the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the same thing with my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He said, it wasn't so bad in the first World War.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had-- we didn't suffer from the German hands.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that was-- that was the main reason, really, which so many people stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
